  Description: You have an incredibly strong connection to the positive energy that
    flows through the First World, making it harder to attack your life force with
    negative energy. You gain negative resistance equal to half your level (minimum
    1). When you have the doomed condition, the condition affects you as if its value
    was 1 lower than it actually is (doomed 1 has no effect, doomed 2 causes you
    to die at dying 3, and so on).
